Detailed Description

This structure contains information required to configure an address translation region.

------------------------------------------------------------------------—

Field Documentation

uint32_t CSL_RatTranslationCfgInfo::baseAddress

The 32-bit base address used in the address comparison

uint64_t CSL_RatTranslationCfgInfo::sizeInBytes

The size of the region (in bytes). If this value is not a power-of-2, it is automatically rounded-up to the next power-of-2 size.

uint64_t CSL_RatTranslationCfgInfo::translatedAddress

The translated address returned on a successful match
